description: AnrPciConflictDrxProfile: This table stores parameters for handling ANR PCI conflict DRX profiles, specifying configuration settings for different cells.  dateTime: Timestamp of the record; Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell; CellId: Unique identifier of the cell; Id2: Redundant cell identifier; Id3:  Unclear identifier (likely internal); vsDataType: Data type identifier; vsDataFormatVersion: Version of data format; AnrPciConflictDrxProfile.anrPciConflictDrxProfileId: Unique ID for the DRX profile; AnrPciConflictDrxProfile.anrPciConflictOnDurationTimer: Timer for ANR PCI conflict duration; AnrPciConflictDrxProfile.anrPciConflictDrxInactivityTimer: Inactivity timer for DRX; AnrPciConflictDrxProfile.anrPciConflictLongDrxCycle: Long DRX cycle configuration.
